'''Black trimmed wizard robes '''are a [[Wizard robes|black wizard robe set]] with a white trim. The pieces are possible rewards from [[Clue scroll (easy)|easy]] [[Treasure Trails]]. This set has the same bonuses as their regular blue counterparts but is worn by players to show a form of wealth.

This set was released on the [[12 June|12th of June,]] [[2014]] along with the [[Treasure Trail]] Expansion update.

